Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.70,0:01:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(宿命之巧遇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.54,0:02:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你回来了，到底如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.08,0:02:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,办理停留的手续十分烦人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.71,0:02:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像在逼我们离开似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.05,0:02:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.05,0:02:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们仍未接到\N帝姆舰队命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.05,0:02:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且外面还有敌军驻守！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.05,0:02:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗什么时候回来？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.99,0:02:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大约2个小时左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.22,0:02:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很重要的事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.49,0:02:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，他说是非常重要的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.86,0:02:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，吩咐他们\N3小时内做好整备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.73,0:02:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,随时出发！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.68,0:02:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀...早知看看\N天气预测表才出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.58,0:03:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.16,0:03:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它真可怜呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.37,0:04:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对...对不起\N我不是存心吓你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.65,0:04:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是说这天鹅...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.35,0:04:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你很喜欢它吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.32,0:04:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界上那有人\N不喜欢美丽的事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.36,0:04:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界上那有人\N不喜欢美丽的事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.99,0:04:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界上那有人\N不喜欢美丽的事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.73,0:04:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人不喜欢吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.70,0:04:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界上那有人\N不喜欢美丽事物的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.00,0:04:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到美丽的东西衰老死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.84,0:04:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不会难过的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.51,0:04:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然会的！是的，小姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.21,0:04:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想请教你一件事！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.01,0:04:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雨停了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.35,0:05:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的眼睛长得很神气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.35,0:05:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.49,0:05:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们可以不理会\N康斯肯的部队吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.56,0:05:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到时再算吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.19,0:05:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德兹尔中将和康斯肯都是一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.00,0:05:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是看眼前的敌人而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.50,0:05:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希莉亚少将却不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.33,0:05:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她能够看透\N整个战局的发展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.84,0:05:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有什么事\N要在卫星六号内办呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.07,0:05:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经很快接近这大战了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.84,0:05:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到时你便会知道的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.85,0:06:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们驶入港口吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.59,0:06:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亚上校的赞斯巴尔\N正在驶入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.52,0:06:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星六号的港口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.36,0:06:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亚？这家伙\N每次都是胡来的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.98,0:06:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界的发展\N真今人意想不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.18,0:06:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然会和敌军\N停在同一个港口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.35,0:06:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有在中立卫星内\N才可办到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.82,0:06:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做戏！\N简直如做戏一样呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.86,0:06:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不如我们\N请吉翁的人一起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.83,0:06:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开派对还好呢！\N说得没错！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.54,0:06:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...我忍耐不了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.17,0:06:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要去那里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.24,0:07:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然是去报仇了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.01,0:07:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杀死良的敌人\N就在眼前...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.84,0:07:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,准人，如果在卫星内开战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.51,0:07:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们会怎样，你知道吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.01,0:07:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不会不知道吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.58,0:07:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.02,0:07:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们就快要离开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.52,0:07:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要禁止所有人擅自出入\N明白吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.65,0:07:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,母舰内应还有\N很多工作尚未完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.12,0:07:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立刻回去自己的岗位吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.82,0:07:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.79,0:07:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望你们\N别再更改停留时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.46,0:07:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.30,0:07:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有武器的封条...\N我知怎做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.30,0:07:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望你们别再和联邦军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.47,0:07:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有任何争执的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.97,0:07:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经交待清楚\N辛苦你了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.98,0:07:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗？你能够\N成为钢弹的驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.02,0:07:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我便开心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.35,0:07:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨晚交给你零件怎样？\N咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.36,0:07:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是我的发明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.53,0:08:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有了它\N会有绝大的效果的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.00,0:08:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的，爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.20,0:08:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的有用？那我成功了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.67,0:08:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要继续再研究\N研究些新发明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.01,0:08:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.65,0:08:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真有用\N我做出来的当然有用！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.80,0:08:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.56,0:09:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那种防空洞\N对空袭是没用的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.99,0:09:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸你认为机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.39,0:09:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比人命更重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.56,0:09:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快搬钢弹上去！   爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.67,0:09:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也快上去白色基地吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.17,0:09:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸...爸爸...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.27,0:09:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了，动不了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.32,0:09:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早知这样就不走这边了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.00,0:09:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.15,0:10:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亚？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.56,0:10:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.82,0:10:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我这位朋友的技术不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.19,0:10:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.73,0:10:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起\N我还以为可以避得过！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.70,0:10:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看要用车拉才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.54,0:10:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你叫什么名？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.18,0:10:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗，我叫阿姆罗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.38,0:10:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗？我好像听过的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.85,0:10:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亚\N我知道你便是夏亚！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.53,0:10:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我来帮手好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.54,0:10:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用了，我自己可以了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.54,0:10:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起\N请问阁下尊姓大名？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.37,0:10:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亚‧阿兹纳布尔\N你看得出来吧，我是个军人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.75,0:11:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亚！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.55,0:11:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉拉！你试试开动它！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.75,0:11:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,记着要慢慢来啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.05,0:11:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道，上校！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.39,0:11:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他真的是夏亚！夏亚...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.22,0:11:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢慢来，知道吗？拉拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.06,0:11:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做什么？退后些，阿姆罗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.70,0:11:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只不过是第一次见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.50,0:11:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为何我会知道\N他就是夏亚？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.57,0:11:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个女孩\N好像是叫做拉拉的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.19,0:11:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你今年几多岁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.85,0:11:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...十六岁！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.52,0:11:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗？真年轻呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.52,0:11:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也了解你面对敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.03,0:11:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心情可能会比较紧张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.53,0:11:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但至少也要说声多谢呢！\N是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.03,0:11:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊...没错！\N多谢你们的帮忙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.23,0:11:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是了...我要走了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.54,0:12:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个少年到底做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.91,0:12:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他一定是听过了\N红色彗星的大名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.38,0:12:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道你是夏亚\N所以怕极了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.22,0:12:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.73,0:12:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事实上，我们来了之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.90,0:12:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是仍和以前一样吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.51,0:12:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来再去想也是一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.17,0:12:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗？中尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.57,0:12:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错，就算再想\N也只是浪费时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.34,0:12:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.71,0:12:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我等了你很久呢\N到底怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.85,0:12:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事实上\N我只可以私人身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.05,0:12:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来帮各位忙的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.69,0:12:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡姆兰...\N那是什么意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.36,0:12:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有艘私人的船...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.36,0:12:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我打算用这个\N送你们出去港口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.03,0:12:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果有这里的船\N就算是吉翁军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.86,0:13:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不会有胆来攻击的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.53,0:13:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样就可安心了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.03,0:13:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡姆兰，到底为了什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.20,0:13:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我为了什么\N难道你还不明白？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.91,0:13:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还要问我？米莱？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.54,0:13:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望你\N别再理我们的事！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.41,0:13:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米莱...既然你\N不肯离开母舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.48,0:13:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最少，你也接受我的好意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.65,0:13:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你根本就没心帮我们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.55,0:13:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你还说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.15,0:13:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样说，简直是侮辱我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.05,0:13:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只是想我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.99,0:13:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,认为你是个了不起的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.36,0:13:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，在我们最困难时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.83,0:13:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你居然不理我们\N还说什么大话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.70,0:13:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是...我的能力\N只能这样而已...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.90,0:13:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那多谢了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.37,0:13:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蠢材！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.67,0:13:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中尉...？               你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.51,0:13:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米莱，他确是诚心诚意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.18,0:13:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还不明白吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.51,0:13:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否则他怎会冒险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.21,0:13:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽说这里是中立国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.35,0:13:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但只要受到导弹的一击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.02,0:13:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也会没命的\N你不明吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.52,0:13:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的为人也是...\N为什么被这样说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.06,0:13:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一句声也不抗辩呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.19,0:14:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用动手\N用口也一样的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.26,0:14:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你觉得愤怒\N便该打她那才是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.93,0:14:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎可以这样粗鲁的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.06,0:14:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗？卡姆兰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.93,0:14:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就认为这是对的\N是吗？中尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.37,0:14:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史列加中尉\N卡姆兰检察官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.37,0:14:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你的提议不变的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.81,0:14:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以帮我们这个忙吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.98,0:14:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！就起出港吧！中尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.17,0:14:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出来了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.33,0:14:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过他们隔邻\N有艘私家船啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.17,0:14:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然有这么无聊的人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.50,0:14:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多姆，出发了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.67,0:14:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该可以出发了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.02,0:15:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,母舰好像改变了航线！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.72,0:15:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想向相反的方向逃走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.59,0:15:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要理侵犯领空的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.02,0:15:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立刻叫多姆出发！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.86,0:15:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫他们在领空外作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.53,0:15:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不可让夏亚小看我的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.98,0:15:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和你说过的条件\N不再作准了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.98,0:15:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要加收费用呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.85,0:15:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.99,0:15:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡姆兰...\N现已到了领空的边界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.69,0:15:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快返回去吧！   我知了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.66,0:15:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点逃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.66,0:15:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.87,0:15:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布莱特，吉翁的MS来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.33,0:15:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知了\N你就送到这里吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.20,0:15:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...可以的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.67,0:15:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要尽力去到最远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.51,0:15:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,究竟发生了什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.68,0:16:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和小孩子没关系的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.35,0:16:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去主炮岗位了   是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.85,0:16:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在已接近\N卫星六号边界了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.86,0:16:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡姆兰！         中尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.49,0:16:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请退后吧！\N我现在要开火了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.30,0:16:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡姆兰，很多谢你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.80,0:16:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我愿意接受你的好意\N不过...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.17,0:16:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之是很多谢你\N卡姆兰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.31,0:16:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你回去吧！\N请代问候你父母！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.68,0:16:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美...米莱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.98,0:16:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们回去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.55,0:16:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托，等一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.66,0:16:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打开大门\N钢弹尽快出动！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.56,0:16:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢加农，G战机\N等候命令！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.17,0:17:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出发！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.51,0:17:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白色基地\N最大战速，对空作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.69,0:17:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.46,0:17:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！多姆队，攻击开始！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.14,0:17:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米加粒子炮，别射向离舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.64,0:17:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否则会打中卫星六号的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.48,0:17:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.98,0:17:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始了，怎办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.65,0:17:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开电视机吧！米莱...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.37,0:18:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.84,0:18:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等我来吧！\N等一会，凯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.04,0:18:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别理会敌军MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.68,0:18:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先阻止敌舰接近就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.48,0:18:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞄准敌舰侧面\N以导弹来防守！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.29,0:18:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看着吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.96,0:18:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没可能，怎会这样的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.30,0:18:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他怎会预计到\N我们的动向...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.30,0:18:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看，巧合而已！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.97,0:18:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我们集合\N一起攻击吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.00,0:18:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.01,0:19:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到了\N我见到他们的行动！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.34,0:19:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的看到了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.11,0:19:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在领空外\N联邦军和吉翁军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.51,0:19:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,双方正在交战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.32,0:19:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别拍白色基地\N快拍钢弹吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.65,0:19:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看他怎样和敌军作战！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.52,0:19:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗到底在干什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.99,0:19:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中尉，他们出来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.36,0:19:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好极，我知道了\N看着吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.54,0:19:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在所见的\N正是一场战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.31,0:19:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,联邦军的母舰正在受到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.38,0:19:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三艘的吉翁的攻击！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.81,0:19:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们打得很激烈呢！\N是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.05,0:20:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要好好看清楚\N真实的战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.05,0:20:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并非如电影般好看的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.36,0:20:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果各位看完了这场战事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.39,0:20:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以后对国家的立场\N应加以讨论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.40,0:20:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.51,0:20:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还收拾不了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.88,0:20:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等...等一会...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.39,0:20:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为何阿姆罗今日的射击\N会这样准？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.69,0:20:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,热能快用完了！\N若不再用枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.70,0:20:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只好用接近战了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.24,0:20:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为何会这样？\N只有一艘战舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.94,0:21:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然费这么大的劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.71,0:21:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亚在看着的\N全力进攻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.08,0:21:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们向着敌方母舰\N的腹部冲过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.53,0:21:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三艘吉翁\N已被联邦军消灭了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.67,0:21:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我觉得白色的\NMS会赢的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.04,0:21:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唔...电视还未\N映出来你也知！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.84,0:21:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知的，若不这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.01,0:21:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上校又怎会收留\N像我这样的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.68,0:21:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉拉你真聪明！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.69,0:21:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们冲过来\N表示他们已着急！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.36,0:21:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底它的要害在那里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.73,0:21:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那里！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.03,0:21:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它来了！         什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.94,0:22:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它已来到下面了！   什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.05,0:22:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看，上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.15,0:22:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错了，阿姆罗\N那就对了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.32,0:22:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是那零件的功能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.66,0:22:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹充份利用它了！哈...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.23,0:22:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球联邦军万岁...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.84,0:22:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以走了，回去吧！   是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.51,0:22:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一定生存下去...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.70,0:23:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,SIDE 7...

